Josh Holloway https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Josh_Holloway 0 Josh Lee Holloway (born July 20, 1969) is an American actor, model and producer, best known for his roles as James "Sawyer" Ford on the American television show Lost and as Will Bowman on the science fiction drama Colony.
